<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: auto auto;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 2rem;
    ">
    <div
      style="
        margin: auto auto;
        background: #fafafa;
        width: 100vw;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 2rem;
      ">
      <img
        style="width: 100%"
        src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1125453534062719016/1162302877507784704/Banner_Ticket.png?ex=653b71e8&is=6528fce8&hm=b97686cec57f00ef08a7b30985c857004429ae330f7fa8b19e53a57afd92992a&" />

      <div style="font-size: 1.2rem">Hi <%= nama %>,</div>
      <div style="margin-top: 1rem">
        Selamat pembelian tiket anda telah berhasil
      </div>
      <div>
        Silahkan unduh tiket untuk
        <b>HIMALAYA: Awarding Night Mr. & Ms. UMN 2023</b>
        pada lampiran email ini
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 1.2rem">
        Jangan lupa untuk hadir pada waktu dan tanggal berikut:
      </div>
      <div style="display: flex">
        <div>
          <div>Waktu Open Gate</div>
          <div>Tanggal</div>
          <div>Tempat</div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-left: 1rem; font-weight: bold">
          <div>: 16.00 - 18.00 WIB</div>
          <div>: 24 November 2023</div>
          <div>: QBIG Convention Hall</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background-color: #fff0a1; padding: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem">
        <div style="font-weight: bold">Tips:</div>
        <div>
          Unduh tiketmu pada lampiran email ini sebelum datang dan menghadari
          acara HIMALAYA: Awarding Night Mr. & Ms. UMN 2023.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 2rem">Rincian Item</div>
      <div style="display: flex">
        <div>
          <div>No Pesanan</div>
          <div>Pesanan</div>
          <div>Jumlah Tiket</div>
          <div>Nama Pemesan</div>
          <div>No. Telephone</div>
          <div>Email</div>
        </div>

        <div style="padding-left: 1rem; font-weight: bold">
          <div>: <%= transaction_id %></div>
          <div>: HIMALAYA: Awarding Night Mr. & Ms. UMN 2023</div>
          <div>: <%= jumlah_ticket %></div>
          <div>: <%= nama %></div>
          <div>: <%= wa %></div>
          <div>: <%= email %></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="https://mrms.umn.ac.id/e-ticket?order_id=<%= transaction_id %>">
        <div
          style="
            margin-top: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
          ">
          <button
            style="
              font-weight: bold;
              background-color: #fff0a1;
              padding: 1rem;
              border-radius: 1rem;
              border: none;
            ">
            Lihat E-Tiket Anda
          </button>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div
      style="
        margin: auto auto;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        width: 100vw;
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: #fafafa;
      ">
      <div style="font-weight: bold">Butuh Bantuan?</div>
      <a
        href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSedPpIfUO3BUyl6p7Cn-CzQqyBzqrSDnfpSbLhzl2HPrN4OaQ/viewform"
        ><div>Form Kendala Tiket Himalaya</div></a
      >
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: auto auto; margin-top: 2rem">
      <img
        style="width: 5rem"
        src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1062052561068228688/1065503219209478184/Logo_Mr___Ms_UMN_2023_-_Circle_copy.png?ex=6539f933&is=65278433&hm=c8b2e66028ddf0407cdad16f335eddbca1c1b3b8006c59232c5abb6f49f2bb27&" />
      <a href="https://mrms.umn.ac.id/ticket-himalaya"
        ><div style="font-weight: bold">
          https://mrms.umn.ac.id/ticket-himalaya
        </div></a
      >
      <div>Copyright â’¸ 2023 Mr. & Ms. UMN. All rights reserved</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>